What is the output?
Path path = Path.of("/user/data/file.txt");
System.out.println(path.getFileName());,file.txt,/user/data/file.txt,data,/user

What happens with serialization?
class Person implements Serializable {
    String name;
    transient int age;
},age is not serialized,Both fields serialized,Compilation error,NotSerializableException

What is the result?
try (FileReader fr = new FileReader("test.txt")) {
    int data = fr.read();
},Character code of first character,First character as String,Entire file content,Compilation error

What is the output?
Path p1 = Path.of("/home/user");
Path p2 = Path.of("docs/file.txt");
System.out.println(p1.resolve(p2));,/home/user/docs/file.txt,docs/file.txt,/home/user,Compilation error

What happens with Files.exists()?
Path path = Path.of("test.txt");
System.out.println(Files.exists(path));,true or false depending on file existence,Always true,Always false,IOException

What is the result?
ObjectOutputStream oos = new ObjectOutputStream(new FileOutputStream("data.ser"));
oos.writeObject(new String("Hello"));,Object serialized successfully,Compilation error,NotSerializableException,String cannot be serialized

What is the output?
Path path = Path.of("/a/b/../c/file.txt");
System.out.println(path.normalize());,/a/c/file.txt,/a/b/../c/file.txt,/a/b/c/file.txt,Compilation error

What happens when serializing an object without Serializable?
class Test {}
ObjectOutputStream oos = new ObjectOutputStream(new FileOutputStream("test.ser"));
oos.writeObject(new Test());,NotSerializableException,Compilation error,Object serialized,IOException

What is the result?
PrintWriter writer = new PrintWriter("output.txt");
writer.println("Hello");
writer.close();,File contains ""Hello"",Compilation error,Nothing written,File is empty

What is the output?
Path path = Path.of("/home/user/docs");
System.out.println(path.getParent());,/home/user,/home,docs,null

What happens with ObjectInputStream?
ObjectInputStream ois = new ObjectInputStream(new FileInputStream("data.ser"));
String s = (String) ois.readObject();,Object deserialized successfully,Compilation error,ClassCastException always,Cannot cast

What is the result?
Path path = Path.of("file.txt");
System.out.println(path.isAbsolute());,false,true,Compilation error,null

What is the output?
Path p1 = Path.of("/home/user/docs");
Path p2 = Path.of("/home/user/pics");
System.out.println(p1.relativize(p2));,../pics,pics,/home/user/pics,Compilation error

What happens with Files.copy()?
Path source = Path.of("source.txt");
Path target = Path.of("target.txt");
Files.copy(source, target);,File copied (if source exists),Always succeeds,Compilation error,Cannot copy files

What is the result?
try (BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new FileReader("test.txt"))) {
    String line = br.readLine();
},First line of file or null,Entire file,Single character,Compilation error

What is the output?
Path path = Path.of("a/b/c");
System.out.println(path.getNameCount());,3,2,1,4

What happens with serialVersionUID?
class Person implements Serializable {
    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
},Used for version control during deserialization,Required for compilation,Prevents serialization,Must be public

What is the output?
Path path = Paths.get("user", "data", "file.txt");
System.out.println(path);,user/data/file.txt (or user\data\file.txt on Windows),user,file.txt,Compilation error

What happens with Console password input?
Console console = System.console();
char[] password = console.readPassword();,Password read without echoing,Password displayed,Compilation error,Returns String

What is the result?
class Parent implements Serializable {}
class Child extends Parent {
    int x = 10;
},Child is serializable,Child needs implements Serializable,Compilation error,NotSerializableException

What happens with try-with-resources?
try (FileInputStream fis = new FileInputStream("test.txt")) {
    // code
},Resource automatically closed,Must close manually,Compilation error,Resource not closed

What is the result?
ObjectOutputStream oos = new ObjectOutputStream(new FileOutputStream("data.ser"));
oos.writeInt(100);
oos.close();,100 written to file,Compilation error,Can only write objects,IOException

What is the output?
Path p1 = Path.of("/a/b/c");
Path p2 = Path.of("/a/b/c");
System.out.println(p1.equals(p2));,true,false,Compilation error,NullPointerException

What is the result?
Path path = Path.of("docs/../file.txt");
System.out.println(path);,docs/../file.txt,file.txt,Compilation error,Path normalized automatically

What is the output?
try (Scanner sc = new Scanner(new File("test.txt"))) {
    System.out.println(sc.nextLine());
},First line of file,Entire file,Compilation error,Single word

What happens with static fields in serialization?
class Test implements Serializable {
    static int count = 10;
},static fields not serialized,static fields are serialized,Compilation error,NotSerializableException

What is the output?
Path path = Path.of("a/b/c/d");
System.out.println(path.getName(1));,b,a,c,d

What is the result?
Path path = Path.of("test.txt");
System.out.println(Files.size(path));,Size of file in bytes,Size in kilobytes,Compilation error,Always 0

What is the output?
Path path = Path.of("docs/data/file.txt");
System.out.println(path.subpath(1, 3));,data/file.txt,docs/data,file.txt,Compilation error

What happens with readObject()?
ObjectInputStream ois = new ObjectInputStream(new FileInputStream("data.ser"));
Object obj = ois.readObject();,Returns deserialized object,Compilation error,Always returns null,Cannot read objects
